This test will check if Blender opens properly from the STUDIO menu.
<dl>
    <dt>Open Blender from the STUDIO menu.</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd>
    <dt>Open the Blender application from GRAPHIC DESIGN subsection in Main Menu.</dt>
        <dd>Blender opens properly.</dd>
</dl>
This test will check if Blender properly saves and re-opens documents.
<dl>
    <dt>Start up Blender</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd> 
    <dt>Add a few mesh-objects to the scene.</dt>
        <dd>Objects are placed on the cursor in the 3d view</dd>
    <dt>Open File-menu,</dt>
	<dt>select</dt>
	<dt>"save as..."</dt>
    <dt>Name the file</dt>
	<dt>pick a location</dt>
	<dt>press</dt>
	<dt>"Save As Blender File"</dt>
        <dd>File is saved.</dd>
    <dt>Open File-menu</dt>
	<dt>select</dt>
	<dt>"Open..."</dt>
    <dt>Pick the previously saved file</dt>
	<dt>press</dt>
	<dt>"Open Blender File</dt>
        <dd>File is opened</dd>
</dl>
This test will check if Blender properly synchronizes with JACK.
<dl>
    <dt>Start Blender</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd>
	<dt>open user preferences</dt>
	<dt>set audio to JACK</dt>
	<dt>save user preferences</dt>
	<dt>quit Blender.</dt>
    <dt>Start QJackCtl</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd> 
    <dt>Start Blender</dt> 
    <dt>Set Blender sync-mode to AV-sync,</dt>
	<dt>press play in Blender</dt>
        <dd>Jack starts running</dd>
    <dt>Focus QjackCtl window</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd>
    <dt>Press "Pause" in QJackCtl</dt>
        <dd>Blender stops</dd>
</dl>
This test will check if Blender properly executes a simple render.
<dl>
    <dt>Start Blender</dt> 
    <dt>Press F12</dt>
        <dd>Blender Renders the start-up scene.</dd>
</dl>

<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
